          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To minimize the uncertainties in the projectile",
                "energies at each target foil, thinly stacked foils with",
                "only three targets were used in each stack.  Aluminium",
                "foils of 6.85 mg/cm**2 were used as energy degraders",
                "and internal flux monitor. For measuring the cross",
                "sections of relatively short-lived nuclides, 1.0",
                "mg/cm**2 thickness 197-Au deposited on Al spacer foils",
                "served as targets. To obtain measurable yields of",
                "long-lived residuals, self-supporting 46.6 mg/cm**2",
                "thick 197-Au targets were used in the stack. Both the",
                "target and the degrader foils were 0F 99.99% purity."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " See SAMPLE"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The irradiation times were optimized according",
                "to half-lives of residual and the irradiations were",
                "performed in duplicate."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The flux values were in good agreement with",
                "flux values obtained from monitor reactions. Their",
                "average was used to determine the cross sections."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The decay of characteristic gamma peaks was",
                "followed for more than five half-lives except for",
                "195-Au for which only two half-lives were followed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error assigned is the root mean square of",
                "the statistical errors associated with the individual",
                "cross sections."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
