          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The excitation functions were analysed in terms",
                "of direct, pre-equilibrium and evaporation emissions.",
                "The two most commonly used models of pre-equilibrium",
                "reactions, the exciton and the hybrid models, have both",
                "been used and compared.  The choice of the initial",
                "exciton number, the role of the pre-equilibrium cluster",
                "and multiple nucleon emissions have been investigated.",
                "The direct emission of cluster are found to",
                "significantly affect the excitation functions of 197-Hg",
                "and Au isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
